{"tid":2373301,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)風雲男人幫 盜海豪情1-3","createTime":"2021-01-20T10:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T18:29:53.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7810d5e7dabb06c30cd18c391d43cf28eafec3d3","tid":2373301,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T10:52:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=32320cc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=a40d415f\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=c9365ac2\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/0/03/Gangster_Squad_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F0%2F03%2FGangster_Squad_Poster.jpg&h=3bfd3392&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://vinnieh.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/oceans-thirteen-cast.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvinnieh.files.wordpress.com%2F2015%2F12%2Foceans-thirteen-cast.jpg&h=4b4328f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.1949年，冷酷無情的黑道老大米奇&middot;柯罕（西恩&middot;潘飾）主宰洛杉磯大小事情，針對被腐敗警界保護的猖獗黑道，警察總長比爾&middot;帕克（尼克&middot;諾特飾）採取了極端手段，他徵召身經百戰的英雄警官約翰&middot;歐馬拉（喬許&middot;布洛林飾）成立一個嚴正的執法小組，他們的工作不是逮捕壞人，而是開戰。當城市爆發了槍戰，疲憊不堪的警官傑瑞&middot;伍特斯（雷恩&middot;葛斯林飾）很不情願地捲入這場對抗之中，因為他愛上被柯恩視為禁臠的優雅尤物葛莉絲&middot;法拉戴（艾瑪&middot;史東飾）<br />\n<br />\n2.從監獄假釋出來後不久，丹尼爾&middot;奧申（喬治&middot;克隆尼飾）與老搭檔拉絲蒂&middot;萊恩（布萊德&middot;彼特飾）就迅速組成了一支專業團隊，要對三家拉斯維加斯賭場貝拉焦、米拉奇和米高梅的金庫下手。這三家賭場都屬於特里&middot;班尼迪克特（安迪&middot;賈西亞飾），共同使用的金庫防護非常嚴密，使用了許多高科技設備。班尼迪克特恰好正在和奧申的前妻苔絲（茱莉亞&middot;羅勃茲飾）約會。隨著劇情發展，奧申提到他帶領這次行動的主要目的就是要重新贏回苔絲的心。富有，卻被班尼迪克特擠出了賭場生意的......<br />\n<br />\n3.三年前丹尼歐遜（喬治克隆尼飾）夥同足智多謀的操盤手羅斯萊恩（布萊德彼特飾）、年輕氣盛的扒手金童萊納斯卡得威（麥特戴蒙飾）、心不在焉的爆破專家拜許（唐其鐸飾），以及鬼計神偷的開鎖高手法蘭克卡頓，一舉幹下史上最膽大妄為、金額最高的竊案，他們設下一場瞞天過海的高明騙局，潛入心狠手辣的黑道賭場老大泰瑞班奈狄掌管的貝拉吉賭場，把他藏在金庫的一億六千萬美元一毛不剩地全都幹走.........<br />\n<br />\n4.魯本&middot;迪什科夫（艾略特&middot;高德飾）患心肌梗塞後，丹尼爾&middot;奧申（喬治&middot;克隆尼飾）等十人圍在他的病床前。四星期前，拉斯維加斯賭場大亨威利&middot;班克（艾爾&middot;帕西諾飾）與魯本在二人合資的新賭場工地中見面。魯本為班克爭取到了關鍵的合同後，班克使出老手段，迫使他交出股份。過度的驚嚇使魯本犯了心臟病。<br />\n奧申等人發誓要為魯本復仇，要在班克的酒店正式開業當晚使其破產。為了達到這個目標，所有的賭客都必須贏錢。由於資金不足，班克在新酒店的建設過程中不得不向一些競爭對手尋求幫助，並將他們安排在了董事會中。如果酒店在第一季度中不能獲利五億美元，班克就會失去他的董事長席位.....<br />\n<br />\n7 05PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=d7e341ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia18MSy0xNzs2bKpftArA8vk%3D&h=61da3b77\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f23d22c52eb5ee2d6c9db42f887fd6efdce1ac","tid":2373301,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b3d41095c7ff4c56c19b1ef5dd8b71e126e67a9","tid":2373301,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T11:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e31025172f2264f6289e540640779e3e9df61fc","tid":2373301,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:11:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb791fc5233a710fa0a103b6384fa1d327b8823","tid":2373301,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T15:32:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9273fbe2345d332f4746858363855d887d4b0bcd","tid":2373301,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T17:02:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0d575e292c375f79ee25bcd9d0e940c38c60d6","tid":2373301,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T18:29:53.000Z"